SIMPLE: whimwham
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whimwham
<hw>Whim"wham</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Formed from
<ets>whim</ets> by reduplication.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>A whimsical thing; an odd device; a trifle; a
trinket; a gimcrack.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>They'll pull ye all to pieces for your <qex>whimwhams</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Bear. & Fl.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A whim, or whimsey; a freak.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whin</ent>⟦br⟧
